{"tid":2200277,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"南區區會追究民政處秘書離席 羅健熙：有種就做晒18區，一次過告擅離職守","createTime":"2020-09-12T21:11:58.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-13T00:11:03.000Z","uid":359022,"like":17,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"71f524be5c446a24fc129d958148b8879b99761d","tid":2200277,"uid":359022,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-12T21:11:58.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.inmediahk.net/node/1077282\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.inmediahk.net%2Fnode%2F1077282&d=O8bnHDCsQiwN1SoPxP513ZmLjsYRFZgpJr%2B2v3iO%2BBA%3D&h=baaf2f89\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.inmediahk.net%2Fnode%2F1077282&h=fc0535e8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.inmediahk.net/node/1077282</a><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\">（獨媒特約報導）</span>南區民政專員鄭港涌上次區議會會議上，不允討論赤柱監獄內聚賭事件及警方處理一名精神上無行為能力的南區居民的手法，之後更帶隊離場。南區區議會副主席司馬文於今日會議上「反擊」，動議討論區議會職能，鄭港涌否認越權，強調赤柱監獄非公眾地方，不屬於區議會討論範圍。會上最終通過由主席羅健熙採取法律行動，跟進民政處秘書離席，羅健熙更斥民政總署「有種就做晒18區秘書，一次過告你擅離職守。」<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"large\"><strong>民政專員稱監獄非公眾地方 拒討論防疫工作</strong></span>"},{"pid":"58e094f4bd244d96ea8f2942f774d83ab5cd6022","tid":2200277,"uid":48060,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-12T21:35:42.000Z","msg":"一早應該啦<br />\n仲忍佢成年呀？"},{"pid":"0c1e3281afab1ea6ad6cee4aed5a2ff86387993f","tid":2200277,"uid":237465,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-13T00:03:50.000Z","msg":"吊上樹再丟臭蛋是嗎 ?"},{"pid":"0d35bcd5cf7cae28e1dfc87a7b8b0ec2190be474","tid":2200277,"uid":3776,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-13T00:11:03.000Z","msg":"就告晒18區"}]}